	handle, as well as a list.

	* mm-view.el (mm-w3m-cid-retrieve-1): Call itself recursively.
	Suggested by ARISAWA Akihiro <ari@mbf.sphere.ne.jp>.
	(mm-w3m-cid-retrieve): Simplify.

